</taxonomicName>
(IRAN 3988C, Ex-Type). On SNA- barley seed, a–f. Conidia. g–k. Solitary, erect, unbranched conidiophores. On infected leaves, l–p. Conidia. q–r. Solitary, erect, unbranched conidiophores. Scale bars = 10 µm.
</paragraph>
